      {/* Faucet indicator (small arc above sink) */}
      <circle cx={hw - width * 0.20} cy={-hd * 0.75}
        r={depth * 0.035} fill="#9E9283" stroke="none" opacity={0.5} />
    </g>
  );
}
```

This provides: 4 burners (architectural convention for cooktops) with dual-ring detail on each, a properly rounded sink basin with subtle blue tint and highlight edge, a drain point, and a faucet indicator.

---

**toilet (700mm x 400mm) -- WC with Cistern and Bowl:**

```jsx
case 'toilet': {
  return (
    <g transform={transform}>
      {/* Cistern: rounded rectangle at back */}
