---

**lavatory (500mm x 400mm) -- Washbasin:**

```jsx
case 'lavatory': {
  const minDim = Math.min(width, depth);
  return (
    <g transform={transform}>
      {/* Outer basin (countertop edge) */}
      <ellipse cx={0} cy={hd * 0.1} rx={width * 0.40} ry={depth * 0.38}
